shared-library patch acl100413 (version 318) ...
Date Posted: -- in testing --
Patch names: acl100413 (version 318), acli100413, libacl100413,
  libacli100413, libacl100413s, libacli100413s, acl100413s,
  acli100413s, libacl100416, libacli100416, acl100416, acli100416,
  libacl100416s, libacli100416s, acl100416s, acli100416s,
  acli10041t3, libacli10041t3
Description: With this patch, global gc of very large spaces will try
  to allocate additional work space to finish the marking phase in
  one pass, before resorting to multiple mark passes. This can reduce
  mark time significantly.
Impact: recommended

