  libacl100416s, libacli100416s, acl100416s, acli100416s,
  acli10041t3, libacli10041t3
Description: Newer OS libraries are using SSE registers, so more
  protection of these registers, commonly used for floating point
  instructions, is necessary. This patch causes these registers to be
  saved and restored where neessary, in order to prevent them from
  being trashed.
Impact: recommended

