aodbc-v2 patch aodbc-v2
Date Posted: Fri Apr 15 11:19:32 PDT 2016
Patch names: code/aodbc-v2.001
Description: Exports two new routines, get-statement-handle and
  free-statement-handle. The return value from get-statement-handle
  can be passed into any routine that accepts an :hstmt keyword
  argument. free-statement-handle should be used to free up hstmt
  resources that will no longer be used.
Impact: recommended

