lisp patch pka010
Date Posted: Sat Dec  5 20:26:27 PST 2015
Patch names: update/pka010.001
Description: Adds extra functionality to allow hash-tables to be
  built with key and value vectors in oldspace or static space. This
  new functionality is not exported or documented; it is transitional
  for 9.0 and 10.0. If you desire to know more, pleas contact Franz
  Inc.
